<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>PSG College of Technology - Summer Internship</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 30px 50px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #000;
      font-size: 11pt;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 14pt; margin: 6px 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 12pt; margin: 4px 0; font-weight: bold; }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }
    td, th {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 6px 8px;
      vertical-align: top;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
    }
    .date-line {
      text-align: right;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    ol {
      margin: 8px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    ol li {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
    }
    .sig-row td {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 40px;
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .principal-block {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 11pt;
    }
    .note {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .note strong { font-weight: bold; }
    p { margin: 6px 0; font-size: 11pt; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</h1>
    <h2>Permission and Undertaking for Summer Internship / Short Duration Internship</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="date-line"><strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}</div>

  <p><strong>From</strong></p>
  <p style="margin-left:0; line-height:1.4;">
    {{student_name}}<br>
    {{roll_number}}<br>
    {{programme}}, Department of {{department}}
  </p>

  <br>

  <p>
    To<br>
    The Principal<br>
    PSG College of Technology<br>
    Coimbatore – 641004
  </p>

  <p>Through :The Head of the Department, Department of {{department}}</p>

  <p>Dear Sir,</p>

  <p><strong>Sub:</strong> Undertaking while pursuing Internship/Project Work II in Industry / Institutions.</p>

  <p>
    I wish to inform that, I have been offered Summer internship/Short Duration internship in the organization, details
    of which are provided below. The activities carried out during this internship will be useful for my placement and
    final year project work.
  </p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:28%; text-align:center;">Name &amp; Address of the Industry / Institution with contact details &amp; Mobile number</th>
        <th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">Internship Period</th>
        <th style="width:22%; text-align:center;">Name of Mentor/ Guide in the Industry &amp; Department</th>
        <th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">Duration for which Attendance needed</th>
        <th style="width:10%; text-align:center;">Stipend receivable (if any)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th></th>
        <th style="text-align:center; width:10%;">From (Date)</th>
        <th style="text-align:center; width:10%;">To (Date)</th>
        <th></th>
        <th style="text-align:center; width:8%;">From</th>
        <th style="text-align:center; width:8%;">To</th>
        <th></th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="text-align:center;"></th>
        <th></th>
        <th></th>
        <th style="text-align:left; font-weight:bold;">Industry<br><br>Department</th>
        <th></th>
        <th></th>
        <th></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <strong>{{company_name}}</strong><br>
          {{company_address}}<br>
          {{company_city}}, {{company_state}}<br>
          {{guide_contact}}
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td>
          <strong>Industry:</strong> {{guide_name_industry}}<br><br>
          <strong>Dept:</strong> —
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">₹ {{stipend_amount}}</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p><strong>My CGPA up to semester _____ is _______</strong></p>

  <p>
    I request you to permit me to accept the offer of the above internship and provide attendance for the duration mentioned.
  </p>

  <p><strong>I hereby undertake the following.</strong></p>

  <ol>
    <li>I will be regular and sincere in carrying out my internship at the above organization and I will obey the Rules and Regulations of the organization.</li>
    <li>I will obtain the attendance certificate and submit the same at academic section within a week from the last date of my internship and also submit the copy of the report of the internship to the HoD.</li>
    <li>I will study on my own, the syllabi covered in the class during my internship.</li>
    <li>Further, after return from internship, I will also complete the assessment components (except CA Test 1 if total CA tests are three) and laboratory experiments missed during the internship period after regular class hours.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the offer letter for internship.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed parent's consent Letter.</li>
  </ol>

  <p style="text-align:right; margin-top:30px;">(Signature of the Student)</p>

  <table style="margin-top:30px; border:none;">
    <tr class="sig-row">
      <td style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; width:16%;">Tutor</td>
      <td style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; width:16%;">Guide (Dept)</td>
      <td style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; width:20%;">Programme Co-ordinator</td>
      <td style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; width:16%;">HoD</td>
      <td style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; width:16%;">Dean (P&amp;T)</td>
      <td style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #000; text-align:center; width:16%;">Dean-Academic</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="principal-block" style="margin-top:30px;">PRINCIPAL</div>

  <div class="note">
    <strong>NOTE:</strong>
    <ol style="margin:4px 0; padding-left:20px;">
      <li>Original Form shall be submitted to <strong>Placement Office</strong> and Photo copies to <strong>Academic Section</strong> and <strong>Head of the Department</strong>.</li>
      <li>If Hostel required during vacation period then separate request letter shall be submitted for the hostel accommodation.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
